descript.abstract: Voting Precincts 2011. The dataset contains polygons representing Plumas County voting precinct boundaries. Precincts were changed based on the 2011 County Supervisorial Redistricting following the 2010 census. Precincts are components of other Election districts and determine where residents vote and in which elective district citizens reside.
descript.purpose: Data created for use in developing a county-wide precincts mapbook. This layer was developed to help the Voter Registrar to determine voting precincts for registered voters in Plumas County for each election period and for general use for public distribution. Precinct boundaries can be overlaid on the GIS parcel layer to designate which voters fall into each precinct.
